name: combo
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "combo" %}
{% set version = "0.1.3" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/combo-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 6536d6d2f0a7a3a136c2127ba82c4bd640fc245c282c2d0060ad49070e57f42a

build:
  noarch: python
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv
  number: 0

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python >=3.6
    - setuptools >=38.6.0
  run:
    - joblib
    - matplotlib-base
    - numba >=0.35
    - numpy >=1.13
    - pyod
    - python >=3.6
    - scikit-learn >=0.20
    - scipy

test:
  imports:
    - combo
  commands:
    - pip check
  requires:
    - pip

about:
  home: https://github.com/yzhao062/combo
  doc_url: https://pycombo.readthedocs.io/
  summary: A Python Toolbox for Machine Learning Model Combination
  license: BSD-2-Clause
  license_file:
    - LICENSE

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - thewchan
